{"root":{"data":{"id":"dja9pzt68vs0","created":1781592186922,"text":"边缘涂装（Edge Coating）","background":"#0070c0","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dja9s7ewz0o0","created":1781592360202,"text":"涂料（Paint）","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dja9sfo8bw80","created":1781592378180,"text":"黏合剂（Adhesion Promoter）","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dja9t0bsdcw0","created":1781592423140,"text":"用途","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djacwbrme2w0","created":1781601146464,"text":"提升剥离强度"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dja9t5e27z40","created":1781592434161,"text":"样式","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dja9t80nc2o0","created":1781592439880,"text":"成分","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dja9z9ztr940","created":1781592914369,"text":"例子","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dja9zcg8lx40","created":1781592919715,"text":"UA400H（粘合性好；浓度比较低适用在反毛皮，而用在超纤容易渗透到皮的表面变黑；浓度低容易吸收，在高吸收性上的皮需要上两次才能均匀上油）\nUA500H（易渗透）\nUA406H\nUA109（油性，气味大，不好操作）","expandState":"expand","layout_right_offset":{"x":57.49999742954992,"y":116.24999480322015}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg1gapnq7k0","created":1782178217873,"text":"COHA871","layout_right_offset":{"x":44.99999798834324,"y":-18.749999161809683}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dja9simp7ns0","created":1781592384617,"text":"底油（Primer）","expandState":"expand","layout_right_offset":{"x":24.999998882413138,"y":31.24999860301608}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dja9tcwsfow0","created":1781592450531,"text":"用途","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dja9tl6lqhs0","created":1781592468539,"text":"样式","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dja9tmgiwrk0","created":1781592471315,"text":"成分","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djb0lb6wqvk0","created":1781667989843,"text":"PU-based"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dja9zhcwcdc0","created":1781592930397,"text":"例子","expandState":"expand","layout_right_offset":{"x":1.1368683772161603e-13,"y":11.249999497085724}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dja9zk3kz480","created":1781592936364,"text":"DA550\nDP5/C","expandState":"expand","layout_right_offset":{"x":59.9999973177911,"y":-2.499999888241234}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg2ihcqz9s0","created":1782181210168,"text":"生物基","layout_right_offset":{"x":23.749998938292265,"y":46.249997932464}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg2ilpx2sg0","created":1782181219671,"text":"DB583"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg2iv6iqu00","created":1782181240266,"text":"饱满度一般\n干燥时间现版本可以，和CA220R1差不多\n烘干容易油小微泡\n硬度可以，和DA550差不多"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dja9sn9c4jc0","created":1781592394693,"text":"色油（边油）（Edge Paint）","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":26.2499988265335,"y":144.99999351799516}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dja9tryhf3s0","created":1781592483285,"text":"用途","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djacwvf9zl40","created":1781601189253,"text":"给皮边上色，形成均匀饱满的有色膜层"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dja9ttg01y00","created":1781592486521,"text":"样式","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg8x7dajhs0","created":1782199290555,"text":"风格","layout_right_offset":{"x":17.499999217689037,"y":1.2499999441206455}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg8xcy450g0","created":1782199302698,"text":"欧洲风格"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg8xwvsgpk0","created":1782199346093,"text":"边油图层较薄，皮层可以容易或明显看到"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg8xf1llk00","created":1782199307262,"text":"美式或亚洲风格 "},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg8ybq2i3k0","created":1782199378399,"text":"边油图层较厚，丰满及圆润，但人造及胶感较中。皮边完全被封闭，不容易看到皮层。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg94ue7qkw0","created":1782199889226,"text":"不同颜色材料类型的边油","layout_right_offset":{"x":7.499999664723873,"y":27.4999987706542}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg952wuago0","created":1782199907766,"text":"颜料型的边油"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg96leudrk0","created":1782200026401,"text":"1、边油的颜色是用颜料膏混合而成\n2、遮盖性较强\n3、无论油多少次，颜色都是稳定一致的"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg957n43880","created":1782199918062,"text":"染料水型的边油","layout_right_offset":{"x":-4.999999776482582,"y":22.49999899417162}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg97b4vgo00","created":1782200082394,"text":"1、边油的颜色是用染料水混合而成\n2、通透性较强，但遮盖性较弱\n3、边油的颜色会随着油边量的改变，越涂越深\n4、LV品牌的皮具产品一般就是用这种类型的边油"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dja9tv0dst40","created":1781592489930,"text":"成分","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":146.24999346211587,"y":88.74999603256595}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djb0lm9z8ew0","created":1781668013974,"text":"聚氨酯型（PU-based）","layout_right_offset":{"x":31.999998897314185,"y":10.49999979883421}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg8zlptckg0","created":1782199478515,"text":"优点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg8zrqybbc0","created":1782199491645,"text":"1、耐寒防爆能力较强\n2、高温高湿环境下的防粘性强\n3、耐曲折能力较强\n4、附着力较强，不容易脱边"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg91cd8jkw0","created":1782199614892,"text":"缺点","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.999999880790824,"y":3.9999998807907104}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg91jqg4mo0","created":1782199630928,"text":"1、价格较高\n2、若产品的黏稠度较高时，气泡较容易产生"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg927ckdxs0","created":1782199682332,"text":"与丙烯酸型的边油的对比","layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":45.99999862909317}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg92m4hzx40","created":1782199714496,"text":"丙烯酸型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg92p4507c0","created":1782199721004,"text":"优点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg92zoy1lc0","created":1782199744030,"text":"1、价格较便宜\n2、若产品的粘稠度较高时，起泡较少"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg92xbdo0w0","created":1782199738856,"text":"缺点","layout_right_offset":{"x":7.499999664723873,"y":39.99999821186054}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg93f2fx0g0","created":1782199777498,"text":"1、耐寒防爆能力较差\n2、高温高湿环境下发黏\n3、耐曲折能力较差\n4、附着力较差，容易脱边"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dja9zozx1gg0","created":1781592947026,"text":"例子","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":22.49999899417162,"y":111.24999502673779}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dja9zqvxb3s0","created":1781592951139,"text":"DAM660","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":61.24999726191163,"y":22.499998994171676}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg2tkh9z7s0","created":1782182078978,"text":"会滴油，容易起泡，有少许凹槽"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg2uvif0oo0","created":1782182181355,"text":"浓度偏高（高于90秒），容易有微泡\n填充性一般，如果下面一层底油打磨不好容易有凹槽\n干燥时间好\n容易沉淀，搅拌不好就有光差问题","layout_right_offset":{"x":74.99999664723885,"y":42.49999810010195}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg2svv2p5c0","created":1782182025393,"text":"DAS660","layout_right_offset":{"x":141.2499936856334,"y":87.49999608844536}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg2tkh9z7s0","created":1782182078978,"text":"会滴油，容易起泡，有少许凹槽"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg2uvif0oo0","created":1782182181355,"text":"浓度偏高（高于90秒），容易有微泡\n填充性一般，如果下面一层底油打磨不好容易有凹槽\n干燥时间好\n容易沉淀，搅拌不好就有光差问题","layout_right_offset":{"x":74.99999664723885,"y":42.49999810010195}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg2t1n17mo0","created":1782182037967,"text":"DES123","layout_right_offset":{"x":192.49999139457987,"y":218.74999022111342}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg2tqgn8vc0","created":1782182092000,"text":"DAH660","layout_right_offset":{"x":171.2499923445289,"y":128.74999424442672}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg2xcqmsww0","created":1782182375586,"text":"会滴油，容易起泡"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg2ea47gww0","created":1782180880957,"text":"生物基","layout_right_offset":{"x":132.74999412521754,"y":338.2499855048959}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg2ew0unt40","created":1782180928644,"text":"DBM790"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg2i8o1mqo0","created":1782181191260,"text":"自然干可以，烘干容易油凹槽\n不容易起泡\n表面比DAM660粗点\n干燥时间可以，大约25分钟自然干（印度条件）","layout_right_offset":{"x":39.99999821186066,"y":-56.249997485429276}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg2f336gso0","created":1782180944022,"text":"DBS790"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg2mtc83ds0","created":1782181549714,"text":"自然干可以，烘干容易油凹槽\n不容易起泡\n表面比DAS660粗点\n干燥时间可以，大约5分钟自然干（印度条件）","layout_right_offset":{"x":84.9999962002039,"y":-8.749999608844519}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg2fhn26740","created":1782180975699,"text":"DBH790","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg1fdwstmo0","created":1782178146471,"text":"防爆油","layout_right_offset":{"x":36.249998379498834,"y":91.24999592080724}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg1fmlt1w80","created":1782178165397,"text":"用途"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg1fpnashk0","created":1782178172018,"text":"样式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg1fqy6xi80","created":1782178174853,"text":"成分"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg1fsqng0g0","created":1782178178751,"text":"例子","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.7499998323618797,"y":18.74999916180971}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg1fudvwaw0","created":1782178182332,"text":"CA226（中光防爆油）\nCOHS602（中光防爆油）","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.7499998323619366,"y":39.99999821186054}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djabprig3540","created":1781597811078,"text":"存储","layout_right_offset":{"x":11.24999949708581,"y":109.99999508261715}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djabptuptgw0","created":1781597816174,"text":"底油与边油","layout_right_offset":{"x":9.999999552965164,"y":26.24999882653367}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djaa0fj98280","created":1781593004792,"text":"操作程序（Operation Procedure）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":193.99999645352403,"y":603.4999730860206},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djaa3yp8rew0","created":1781593281605,"text":"一般流程（对于皮边厚度≤3mm）","layout_right_offset":{"x":71.75001020356956,"y":-54.499997667968614},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djaa79ewfiw0","created":1781593540017,"text":"黏合剂（apply adhesion promoter）→底油（apply 1st primer）→打磨（buff）→底油（apply 2nd primer）→打磨（buff）→色油（apply 1st colored edge paint）→色油（apply 2nd colored edge paint）","layout_right_offset":{"x":126.75001018866863,"y":2.750000905245315},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg2y3b41bc0","created":1782182433421,"text":"干燥","layout_right_offset":{"x":27.499998770654088,"y":97.49999564141046}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg32va9qug0","created":1782182807776,"text":"黏合促进剂","layout_right_offset":{"x":16.249999273568392,"y":-26.24999882653367}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg33ogd6eo0","created":1782182871271,"text":"时间","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg33s8i1yw0","created":1782182879503,"text":"自然干燥","layout_right_offset":{"x":11.24999949708581,"y":-7.499999664723987}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3ausslkw0","created":1782183433633,"text":"10-15分钟"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg4mqyzr1s0","created":1782187186780,"text":"红外线及烘箱","layout_right_offset":{"x":6.999999791383516,"y":10.999999672174567}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg4mwgvh5s0","created":1782187198745,"text":"5分钟"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg346u5nb40","created":1782182911287,"text":"温度及湿度条件","layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":24.999998882413024}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg33s8i1yw0","created":1782182879503,"text":"自然干燥","layout_right_offset":{"x":7.499999664723873,"y":-4.999999776482696}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3ayexyqo0","created":1782183441502,"text":"25-35℃；65%或以下"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg4nqrb9nk0","created":1782187264680,"text":"红外线及烘箱"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg4nwwdrs80","created":1782187278047,"text":"45-50℃；30%或以下"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg3442qv5s0","created":1782182905276,"text":"第一层底油","layout_right_offset":{"x":42.49999810010195,"y":112.49999497085821}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg399mcvoo0","created":1782183309167,"text":"时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":14.999999329447974,"y":6.499999694526309}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg39kv7xz40","created":1782183333648,"text":"自然干燥","layout_right_offset":{"x":13.999999582767487,"y":-37.99999886751186}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3cupac6g0","created":1782183590149,"text":"40-50分钟"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg39uwwf4g0","created":1782183355517,"text":"烘干","layout_right_offset":{"x":19.99999940395378,"y":-13.999999582767487}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3a0dtugg0","created":1782183367424,"text":"第一自然干10-15分钟\n第二烘干20分钟\n第三冷却10-15分钟","layout_right_offset":{"x":11.249999497085582,"y":12.499999441206683}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg39b5g50g0","created":1782183312498,"text":"温度及湿度条件","layout_right_offset":{"x":20.99999929964565,"y":47.49999802559614}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3am86cxk0","created":1782183414972,"text":"烘干"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3bi989kw0","created":1782183484693,"text":"45-50℃：30%或以下"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg3b6p0u3k0","created":1782183459526,"text":"自然干燥"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3bgiukzs0","created":1782183480921,"text":"25-35℃；65%或以下"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg3b88sqjs0","created":1782183462899,"text":"冷却"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3b9k2bpc0","created":1782183465757,"text":"25-35℃；65%或以下"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg346u5nb40","created":1782182911287,"text":"第二层底油","layout_right_offset":{"x":36.249998677521944,"y":210.9999910295013}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg399mcvoo0","created":1782183309167,"text":"时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33.99999876320385,"y":6.499999694526309}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg39kv7xz40","created":1782183333648,"text":"自然干燥"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3cupac6g0","created":1782183590149,"text":"50-60分钟"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg39uwwf4g0","created":1782183355517,"text":"烘干"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3a0dtugg0","created":1782183367424,"text":"第一自然干10-15分钟\n第二烘干20分钟\n第三冷却10-15分钟","layout_right_offset":{"x":11.249999497085582,"y":12.499999441206683}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg39b5g50g0","created":1782183312498,"text":"温度及湿度条件","layout_right_offset":{"x":20.99999929964565,"y":47.49999802559614}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3am86cxk0","created":1782183414972,"text":"烘干"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3bi989kw0","created":1782183484693,"text":"45-50℃：30%或以下"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg3b6p0u3k0","created":1782183459526,"text":"自然干燥","layout_right_offset":{"x":25.999999225139845,"y":20.99999937415123}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3bgiukzs0","created":1782183480921,"text":"25-35℃；65%或以下","layout_right_offset":{"x":4.999999850988388,"y":0}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg3b88sqjs0","created":1782183462899,"text":"冷却","layout_right_offset":{"x":19.99999940395378,"y":26.999999195337296}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3b9k2bpc0","created":1782183465757,"text":"25-35℃；65%或以下","layout_right_offset":{"x":23.999999284744263,"y":8.999999731779099}},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg6qkq03vc0","created":1782193128853,"text":"第一层色油","layout_right_offset":{"x":57.99999797344208,"y":355.9999891668565}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg399mcvoo0","created":1782183309167,"text":"时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33.99999876320385,"y":6.499999694526309}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg39kv7xz40","created":1782183333648,"text":"自然干燥"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3cupac6g0","created":1782183590149,"text":"50-60分钟"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg39uwwf4g0","created":1782183355517,"text":"烘干"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3a0dtugg0","created":1782183367424,"text":"第一自然干10-15分钟\n第二烘干20分钟","layout_right_offset":{"x":11.249999497085582,"y":12.499999441206683}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg39b5g50g0","created":1782183312498,"text":"温度及湿度条件","layout_right_offset":{"x":20.99999929964565,"y":47.49999802559614}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3am86cxk0","created":1782183414972,"text":"烘干"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3bi989kw0","created":1782183484693,"text":"45-50℃：30%或以下"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg3b6p0u3k0","created":1782183459526,"text":"自然干燥","layout_right_offset":{"x":25.999999225139845,"y":20.99999937415123}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3bgiukzs0","created":1782183480921,"text":"25-35℃；65%或以下","layout_right_offset":{"x":4.999999850988388,"y":0}},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg6qkq03vc0","created":1782193128853,"text":"第二层色油","layout_right_offset":{"x":45.499998532235395,"y":467.2499841935937}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg399mcvoo0","created":1782183309167,"text":"时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":75.24999691918515,"y":16.4999992474917}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg39kv7xz40","created":1782183333648,"text":"自然干燥","layout_right_offset":{"x":11.24999949708581,"y":1.2499999441206455}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3cupac6g0","created":1782183590149,"text":"50-60分钟"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg39uwwf4g0","created":1782183355517,"text":"烘干","layout_right_offset":{"x":13.7499993853271,"y":7.499999664723873}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3a0dtugg0","created":1782183367424,"text":"第一自然干10-15分钟\n第二烘干20分钟","layout_right_offset":{"x":11.249999497085582,"y":12.499999441206683}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg39b5g50g0","created":1782183312498,"text":"温度及湿度条件","layout_right_offset":{"x":40.99999840557621,"y":67.49999713152647}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3am86cxk0","created":1782183414972,"text":"烘干"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3bi989kw0","created":1782183484693,"text":"45-50℃：30%或以下"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg3b6p0u3k0","created":1782183459526,"text":"自然干燥","layout_right_offset":{"x":25.999999225139845,"y":20.99999937415123}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg3bgiukzs0","created":1782183480921,"text":"25-35℃；65%或以下","layout_right_offset":{"x":4.999999850988388,"y":0}},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg6xzf4lq00","created":1782193709396,"text":"注意","layout_right_offset":{"x":42.99999575316906,"y":605.2499825097623}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg6y8cy24g0","created":1782193728855,"text":"油每层底油或边油的等待时间不要超过4小时，因为过长的等待时间会影响层与层间的粘合力，导致脱落的风险很高。如果等待时间超过4小时，油下一层底油或色油前需要先轻轻打磨一次。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg71htvn800","created":1782193984562,"text":"油下一次边油或打磨前，必须判断边油是否足够干透，由于干燥时间受天气条件和湿度的影响，所以干燥时间应适当调整以确保到百年有足够干透。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg75llkpb40","created":1782194306224,"text":"备注"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg75n1mu080","created":1782194309372,"text":"确保部件开料平整，没有粗糙。否则，油第一次粘合剂或底油前需要打磨或打砂，以使部件表面平整光滑。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg780q5e3k0","created":1782194495881,"text":"所有部位及物料上必须使用粘合剂。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg787u6w3s0","created":1782194511363,"text":"所有油好边油的部件需要最少自然干2到3小时，才可进行下一个工序。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg78xmq6xk0","created":1782194567508,"text":"完成油边后，如果成品在正常天气条件下（~25-35℃，RH~60-70%）晾干，建议在48-48小时后进行包装。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg79yx9ozs0","created":1782194648686,"text":"所有边油测试建议应在涂好边油48小时后才进行，因为所有化工品都需要时间去作固化。虽然使用烘干机表面好像干了，但实则未干透固化，所以建议最好在48小时后才作包装或测试。"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg0dn70ja80","created":1782175188841,"text":"判断边油是否干透的方法","layout_right_offset":{"x":126.83332804259373,"y":727.4166315044811}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg0e4oj4v40","created":1782175226906,"text":"方法1：砂纸测试"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg0giwtysg0","created":1782175414611,"text":"用#240号砂纸在边油表面轻轻用手打磨，如果打磨中所产生的尘粉是粉末状，则代表边油干透"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg0g9ykiqw0","created":1782175395125,"text":"方法2：湿度检测仪测试"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg10dxjpbk0","created":1782176971053,"text":"使用湿度检测仪测试边油的表面，如果测试仪显示11-12%或更低，则表示边油干透"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg7jni4w740","created":1782195407468,"text":"调颜色","layout_right_offset":{"x":81.99999755620956,"y":911.9999749660496}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg7jusjkr40","created":1782195423335,"text":"1、滴入适量的色浆至边油\n2、使用干净专用的棒子将边油均匀搅拌"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg99t6l8zk0","created":1782200278409,"text":"错误操作","layout_right_offset":{"x":46.66666342152507,"y":1063.333259390464},"priority":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djab5ceqvqw0","created":1781596210920,"text":"工具","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-1303.333243942928,"y":-703.7499509068855},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djaakzgae680","created":1781594615432,"text":"油边工具","expandState":"expand","layout_left_offset":{"x":-34.999998435378075,"y":11.249999497085838}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djaala3vkn40","created":1781594638626,"text":"油轮","layout_right_offset":{"x":39.99999821186054,"y":-12.499999441206342},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-5.9999998211861225,"y":-62.999998122453746}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djaao2xep6o0","created":1781594858090,"text":"粗齿轮油轮用于底油，幼齿轮邮轮用于粘合促进剂及色油\n（号码#越大，齿轮越幼）","layout_right_offset":{"x":41.24999815598119,"y":-18.749999161809797},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-20.99999937415123,"y":-25.999999225139675}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djaaqh4p8k00","created":1781595045734,"text":"原因"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djaaqmg7up40","created":1781595057314,"text":"幼细的油斗可以帮助减少饱和滴油的问题"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djaau25cms00","created":1781595326578,"text":"双边自动油边机","layout_right_offset":{"x":26.249998826533556,"y":6.249999720603341},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-64.99999806284916,"y":-37.99999886751169}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djab1lyjaqo0","created":1781595918251,"text":"建议速度：3-4"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djb0ffgl1xk0","created":1781667528951,"text":"直式油边机（两边）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-130.99999609589588,"y":-40.99999877810484},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djb0div2beg0","created":1781667379628,"text":"1、边油倒入两旁的油缸\n2、将皮条放入中间，然后慢慢地将底部接回\n3、将皮条晾干","layout_left_offset":{"x":-109.99999672174465,"y":24.999999254941883}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djaazkwjt540","created":1781595759226,"text":"自动型油盒","layout_right_offset":{"x":63.749997150153064,"y":27.4999987706542},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-63.999998092651424,"y":12.999999612569923}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djaazuhwte80","created":1781595780108,"text":"建议不要使用胶油轮，改用金属油轮"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djab07u1t7c0","created":1781595809140,"text":"油轮滚动速度不要太快，容易导致很多气泡"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djab0vmfd7c0","created":1781595860922,"text":"建议速度\n底油：3-4\n色油：2-3"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djay223xvn40","created":1781660838934,"text":"自动油边机（电动油边机）工序","layout_left_offset":{"x":-142.49999407678888,"y":17.249999169260377}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djay2b1449k0","created":1781660858354,"text":"1、将边油倒入油缸\n2、盖上挡板\n3、调整挡板和油边轮之间的宽度来控制油量\n4、去除泡泡\n5、拉动皮条涂上边油","layout_left_offset":{"x":-47.499997876584644,"y":-8.749999608844519}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djb0gr653qw0","created":1781667632805,"text":"全自动边油调色","layout_left_offset":{"x":-56.999998301267624,"y":182.9999945461753}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djb0ia4pyig0","created":1781667752442,"text":"1、测色仪读取颜色\n2、分析及生成配方\n3、调色机按配方加入颜料\n4、搅拌均匀并检查颜色，继续调整直至颜色相符","layout_left_offset":{"x":-212.99999089539097,"y":1.4999995455147825}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djb0s2h72q00","created":1781668519423,"text":"加入助剂","layout_left_offset":{"x":-87.49999608844519,"y":168.7499924562872},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djb0sr425mo0","created":1781668573049,"text":"1、确保宽口桶干净\n2、将边油完全倒入一宽口桶\n3、取适量的增稠剂（0.05-0.1%，按要求浓度调整）\n4、取适量消泡剂（0.1-0.5%）\n5、再取适量的纯净水（1-3%）\n6、用搅拌机或一专用棍子顺一方向边搅拌边慢慢加入\n7、搅拌3-5分钟，静置2小时后再使用","layout_left_offset":{"x":-544.9999796599158,"y":-69.99998834729257}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djab23qczyg0","created":1781595956938,"text":"备注","layout_right_offset":{"x":47.499997876584644,"y":33.74999849125754},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-260.2499905116863,"y":-117.2499957419933},"progress":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djab2a254co0","created":1781595970712,"text":"由于不同工厂的工具来自不同的供应厂商，参数应根据具体情况设定。","layout_right_offset":{"x":39.999998211860714,"y":0},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-56.000000327825546,"y":-2.2500008083881085}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djab6faylfk0","created":1781596295585,"text":"打磨工具","layout_left_offset":{"x":-241.49999075382988,"y":192.49999400228285}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djab6onrreg0","created":1781596315951,"text":"皮毯轮（Leather and felt flap wheel）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-128.74999424442672,"y":-67.49999698251497}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djab7hj3nls0","created":1781596378795,"text":"毛毯轮（Felt wheel）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-221.24999010935454,"y":2.499999888241291}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djab80e3hgg0","created":1781596419852,"text":"纤维轮（Fiber wheel）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-212.49999050050997,"y":57.499997429549694}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djab8noiac80","created":1781596470547,"text":"羊毛轮（wool wheel） ","layout_left_offset":{"x":-249.99998882412945,"y":113.74999491497897}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabeyfwvxc0","created":1781596964157,"text":"#120打磨石轮","layout_left_offset":{"x":-266.2499880976979,"y":161.2499927915636}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabf5h0li00","created":1781596979461,"text":"装上砂纸的软砂轮","layout_left_offset":{"x":-289.9999870359902,"y":196.24999256804608}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabfjkotfc0","created":1781597010158,"text":"装上砂纸的砂轮","layout_left_offset":{"x":-282.49998737126646,"y":232.4999896064404}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabggjwtlk0","created":1781597081945,"text":"注意事项","layout_left_offset":{"x":-251.2499887682502,"y":292.4999869242314}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djabgwhel4o0","created":1781597116622,"text":"打磨轮须保持良好状态，必要时更换。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabh6h4u000","created":1781597138373,"text":"保持打磨轮清洁，打磨后用微湿毛巾擦干净打磨轮，因为残留的灰尘会沾到边油上。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djabio75j8o0","created":1781597255316,"text":"烘干工具","layout_left_offset":{"x":-103.9999960064888,"y":409.9999750256539}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djabiv7uzi00","created":1781597270596,"text":"流水线输送带烘干机"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabizvd58w0","created":1781597280725,"text":"自动旋转式烘干机"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabj65bmaw0","created":1781597294387,"text":"发热头移动式烘干机","layout_left_offset":{"x":-7.49999966472393,"y":13.7499993853271}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabjkt50680","created":1781597326303,"text":"高空吊篮运输带","layout_left_offset":{"x":-18.749999161809683,"y":36.00000804662693}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabjrawdrs0","created":1781597340437,"text":"焗炉/烤箱","layout_left_offset":{"x":-55.999997287988776,"y":100.99999557435513}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djabknxmn9s0","created":1781597411469,"text":"没有时间控制，难把控时间，容易过度烘干"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djabm3qutio0","created":1781597524252,"text":"注意事项","layout_left_offset":{"x":-0.9999992996455376,"y":159.49999304860864}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djabm9bjpi80","created":1781597536387,"text":"温度调到45-50℃，过高会产生气泡，甚至造成黏合问题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabmtcroq80","created":1781597579996,"text":"烘干机内理想湿度应低于20%","layout_left_offset":{"x":-41.249998155981416,"y":3.749999832361823}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabn7azxfs0","created":1781597610364,"text":"定期检查烘干机内实际温度和预设温度是否相同","layout_left_offset":{"x":-27.499998770654315,"y":11.249999497085582}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djabnhd7c5s0","created":1781597632266,"text":"烘干机内实际温湿度满足最佳温度和湿度时，烘干时间约为20分钟。（根据具体设备而定）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-7.499999664723873,"y":18.749999161809683}},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djb65cyi3340","created":1781683666521,"text":"皮革类型","layout_mind_offset":{"x":1065.4166390891705,"y":2604.083233861049}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djb6kxu69340","created":1781684887435,"text":"人造革","expandState":"expand","layout_left_offset":{"x":-54.99999754130852,"y":4.999999776482582}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djb6gupj8g00","created":1781684567167,"text":"PU皮（二代皮）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-135.9999959468842,"y":-11.999999642372131}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djb6h8l4sjk0","created":1781684597376,"text":"以聚氨酯（PU, polyurethane）为原料制成的人造皮革","layout_left_offset":{"x":-13.249999660998697,"y":-15.749999772757292}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djb6l9arulc0","created":1781684912383,"text":"PVC皮（一代皮）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-113.99999660253548,"y":-119.99999642372131}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djb6lnyrrx40","created":1781684944309,"text":"超纤（microfiber）（超细纤维PU合成革）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-112.99999663233763,"y":29.74999935552478},"layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":2.499999888241291}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djbqi9xedr40","created":1781741100857,"text":"真皮","layout_left_offset":{"x":-64.99999709427362,"y":126.24999435618543},"layout_right_offset":{"x":41.24999815598153,"y":28.749998714774847}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djbqjqmb00w0","created":1781741215555,"text":"头层皮","layout_left_offset":{"x":-28.74999871477496,"y":-24.99999888241291}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djbqjutzehs0","created":1781741224727,"text":"二层皮","layout_left_offset":{"x":-29.999998807907104,"y":59.999997317790985}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djbqkal4uuo0","created":1781741259020,"text":"鞣制方式","layout_left_offset":{"x":-59.9999973177911,"y":282.4999873712661},"layout_right_offset":{"x":39.99999821186111,"y":68.74999692663584}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djbqkkwie9c0","created":1781741281476,"text":"植鞣","layout_left_offset":{"x":-15.999999523162899,"y":0}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djbqkp2f8uw0","created":1781741290540,"text":"铬鞣","layout_left_offset":{"x":-21.999999344348964,"y":33.99999898672104}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg7qfyf1rs0","created":1782195939587,"text":"测试","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-286.6666467322252,"y":1680.666550073365}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg7qw2cqm00","created":1782195974654,"text":"边油附着力测试","layout_left_offset":{"x":-158.49999404698576,"y":294.74998840317176}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg7usmb3ds0","created":1782196280610,"text":"准备","layout_left_offset":{"x":-34.99999895691883,"y":-57.9999982714653}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg7v2agky00","created":1782196301661,"text":"1、用干净的布蘸汽油把要粘上皮条的PVC条的一面清洁干净\n2、在粘合板表面均匀涂一层薄薄的粘合剂，将试样边油层朝下放在粘合板上，两端各留出15毫米，然后将加重块压在试样上2分钟以上，待自然干2小时","layout_left_offset":{"x":-97.99999037385015,"y":-4.999999850988161}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg82w7wtt40","created":1782196915360,"text":"测试程序","layout_left_offset":{"x":-109.99999672174476,"y":-3.9999998807907104}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg82zex5740","created":1782196922314,"text":"1、沿着整条试样的五个等距位置处测量试样的宽度精确至0.05厘米。记录五个读数的平均值（W）\n2、将夹爪固定在拉力机的下夹具中，然后将试样（粘了边油条的PVC条）滑入下面的夹爪\n3、用上面的夹爪夹住突出来的边油皮条，与PVC条成约90°的角度\n4、以100±5毫米/分钟的夹爪分离速度接通拉力机，机器应该开始记录试样与边油分离的力距图。 分离到约30毫米至35毫米停止和松开样品。检查测试结果，并打印出报告。\n\n于每个试样，测定所有峰的平均值精确至0.1牛顿（L）\n\n要求标准：≥ 25牛顿/厘米\n若测试结果的平均值 ≥ 25牛顿/厘米 → 合格\n若测试结果的平均值 < 25牛顿/厘米 →不合格","layout_left_offset":{"x":-118.2500024475155,"y":19.249998811632622}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djg8mhvdtfs0","created":1782198451411,"text":"对比测试性能","layout_left_offset":{"x":-136.7499957941477,"y":-341.2499898113315}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djg8muw680w0","created":1782198479757,"text":"干燥时间"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8nb32moo0","created":1782198515002,"text":"粘度"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8ntd8blk0","created":1782198554799,"text":"外观"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8nuhk1m80","created":1782198557237,"text":"色差"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8nvjzxgg0","created":1782198559561,"text":"丰满度"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8nwxko9s0","created":1782198562559,"text":"消泡性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8o49phpc0","created":1782198578530,"text":"光泽度"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8o9yb0w00","created":1782198590901,"text":"抗流性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8oekehwg0","created":1782198600945,"text":"干爽性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8r6xyuzc0","created":1782198819443,"text":"上油量"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8rbvpn7c0","created":1782198830191,"text":"打磨性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8re2bneg0","created":1782198834944,"text":"拉伸性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djg8rjex7mo0","created":1782198846590,"text":"粗细度"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue-compat","version":"1.4.43"}